opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 16th day of October, 2013, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED, and the Petition for Writ of Habeas Corpus is DENIED. The Prothonotary is directed to strike the name of the jurist from the caption.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
